 Life walked around the alliance base. He had to get used to his knew 
surrondings. He walked onto the bridge and looked around to see if there was 
anyone there.
 ::Destructor::
    He heard Kit Kat enter. He ran back. And saw the three other bots.."Did 
you get my mess my leader?"
